    "detail": "Location is very convenient, and it is just 8-10mins walk to myeongdong, Near to namsan tower too. There are quite a few of hip cafes around the hotel area, and it is very convenient if you'd like to grab a cup of coffee when you are on the way back after a long shopping day. It is connected to eujilro-il to eiljiro sam ga station, you can walk up from the underground pass link to the subway and 1-2 mins walk to the hotel. I like this hotel, and will book this hotel for my next visit to Seoul :)) ",
